Troubleshooting Tips
Neo4j Connection Issues:

Ensure Neo4j service is running: sudo systemctl restart neo4j
Check port 7474 is accessible: netstat -tlnp | grep 7474
Verify credentials are correct (neo4j/bloodhound123)
Python Import Errors:

Install missing packages: pip3 install ldap3 neo4j
Check Python version: python3 --version (should be 3.6+)
BloodHound GUI Not Starting:

Verify X11 forwarding if using SSH: echo $DISPLAY
Check BloodHound binary permissions: chmod +x BloodHound
Review logs: journalctl -u neo4j -n 50
